Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個人的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是無法重疊在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這樣下去是不行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷 之後就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙 想要逃掉值日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫逃掉 這本來就不是我們該做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊 別讓我們把話挑明了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想把活都推給天枷同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由夢 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏學姐也說過人對待事物經常是三分鐘熱度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於天枷的事 雖然我也想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們能做的 也只有靜觀動向而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說不要擅自行動 先靜觀其變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騷動過一段時間自然消失也不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 之後一段時間內 天枷的事暫時由我負責
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟啟動了天枷的人是我 我必須承擔責任才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我估計會有一段時間不能來參加樂隊的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解 如果有難處你可一定要跟我們說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想幫天枷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在就請交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡天枷的人 也會敵視她身邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓小戀遇到危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 由夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻內 美夏一個人能回家的 別擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我當傻瓜 美夏我可是最尖端科技的結晶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們竟然把我當小孩看待…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在這裡在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 義之君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學也在呢 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個提議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提議？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學 這段時間 要不要成為我們家的一員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家的一員？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這件事解決之前 讓她一直在我們家住下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟還是小心一點的好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又讓你費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是謝謝你的好意 還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這可是校長命令哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣確實挺好的呢 對吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就這麼決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定？ 就這麼決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 小戀呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看搞笑Gong Show
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看歌曲Top10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看搞笑Gong Show
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看歌曲Top10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看搞笑Gong Show
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看歌曲Top10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定看這個了吧 櫻內
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 由夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷 你在別人家就不知道客氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你用不著這麼說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 美夏可是因為校長一直嘮叨個不停才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之便是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你就想這麼隨便地招呼客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說得非常對 那麼就請隨意看你們喜歡的節目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻內 你擋著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡天枷的人 也會敵視她身邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓小戀遇到危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 便當？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想讓大家一起吃所以做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學喜歡的香蕉三明治也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思呢 讓你這麼費心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 快來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學又…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 小戀呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 沒跟你在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒有社團活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}From奈奈佳  知道小戀在哪裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也確實是想要休息了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有義之君的社團活動 就像是沒有草莓的草莓蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}To奈奈佳  就別去打擾她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息的理由也並不是因為這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天沒去社團活動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈佳發短信給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 是因為我的原因吧 昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為昨天不在狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以怕奈奈佳說我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在狀態？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 別擔心 我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 瞭解了 要我去跟涉也說一聲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事 我會跟他說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候才能給我個答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷美夏那件事 再怎麼謹慎認真也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也回應的太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也解決不了問題 我就用我的方式來做出回應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會向PTA和教育委員會提出異議
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}PTA：家長教師會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直這麼含糊搪塞可不是辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音姬 你真的不知情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音姬 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由紀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由紀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士最後…了卻了自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤井同學 因為機器人才讓家庭支離破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還被奪去了自己的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直是這樣認為的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台灣香蕉和厄瓜多爾香蕉 要哪種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻內 隨便哪個都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一個香蕉素比較多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然連學生會那邊都串通過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 我沒有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管櫻內你做什麼 我都絕對不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器人 機器人我絕對不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下 不是你接不接受的問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣 很瞭解班長的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不全是機器人的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底瞭解什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種人到底能瞭解什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然之間就失去了父親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直傷心 痛苦著 什麼辦法也想不出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能一直這麼哭 你怎能體會我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器人把我的一切都奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因為這個 我 我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 謝謝你了 勇鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你們是姐姐的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我叫澤井勇鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是懂禮貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們走吧 勇鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是第一次知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長有那麼小的一個弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤井會生氣也是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡還有個這麼大的孩子呢 現在被機器人搞得一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣也是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那些事和天枷一點關係都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏至今為止沒有相信過任何一個人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說是憎恨人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類只顧自己方便製造出了機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妨礙自己的生活 馬上就毫不猶豫地廢棄掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信人類很險惡 機器人總是扮演著被害者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 我犯了一個非常大的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有因機器人而遭到不幸的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像澤井那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏是機器人 澤井是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但澤井和以前的美夏是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資本主義經濟的發展使社會的構成變得更為複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}當經濟處於衰退時期 就業者數量下降 收入的減少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}在這不容樂觀的形勢下 個人收入的變化量也無法與之同步…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷雖然是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 還是得想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}至此 有分析指出這個問題必須由社會與國家相結合來進行解決
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}也就誕生了社會保障問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}日後 社會保障制度…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}From奈奈佳  看外面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是沒問題了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃些 多吃些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學的事能平安解決就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀 看你一臉寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得義之做得很對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…那個…寂寞什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是瞞不過奈奈佳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是義之君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去開門哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:20:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈佳 那個 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得義之為了天枷同學這麼努力是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真心這麼想的 但是 正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望義之為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之為我操心 雖然很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望可以幫義之一把
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和義之一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是戀人 我想兩個人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻隱藏著自己真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還撒了「不想讓義之為難」 這樣的謊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直這麼壓抑著自己 一直挑義之愛聽的話說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣根本就不是我 不是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和義之交往以前 還沒有這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係本應比青梅竹馬更進了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在和義之在一起好痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 我會討厭自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會開始討厭義之的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀 很難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也許已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}嘴裡叼著麵包說著遲到了遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}在拐角撞到的人是轉學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}遇到這種女生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}會說神啊 這種事還真是難碰上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}嗯？倒不是說多討厭…
